    "content": {
        "data": "{\"textPanel\":{\"list\":[{\"title\":\"目的\",\"data\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">探究高吸水性树脂的吸水性能</span></span></span></span></span></p>\\n\"},{\"title\":\"用品\",\"data\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">实验仪器：电子天平</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">、</span>100</span></span><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">ml</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">烧杯&times;4</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">，</span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">玻璃棒&times;2，镊子</span></span></span></span></span></p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">实验药品：蒸馏水</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">，</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">高吸水性树脂，脱脂棉</span></span></span></span></span></p>\\n\"},{\"title\":\"步骤\",\"data\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">在</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">100</span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">ml</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">烧杯中放入</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">70</span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">ml</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">水</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">，</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">再放入1袋</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">高吸水性树脂，称量质量（</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">m</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">₁</span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">）</span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">，</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">用玻璃棒充分均匀搅拌后静置</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">，</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">观察和记录现象</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">。</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">倾出未被吸收的水（</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">若水被完全吸收，则继续加水直至树脂无法吸水后倾出剩余水），再</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">称出吸收水后的高吸水性树脂的质量</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">（</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">m</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">₂</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">），</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">计算其吸水率</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri; font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">。</span></span></span></span></p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">取</span>1块<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">脱脂棉，按上述方法进行实验，并计算出它的吸水率，与高吸水性树脂的吸水率进行比较。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;</p>\\n\"},{\"title\":\"数据\",\"data\":\"<table cellspacing=\\\"0\\\" class=\\\"MsoTableGrid\\\" style=\\\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none; font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size:13px; text-align:justify\\\">\\n\\t<tbody>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td style=\\\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:142px\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">吸水材料</span></span></span></span></span></p>\\n\\t\\t\\t</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td style=\\\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:142px\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">高吸水性树脂</span></span></span></span></span></p>\\n\\t\\t\\t</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td style=\\\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:142px\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">一般吸水材料</span></span></span></span></span></p>\\n\\t\\t\\t</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td style=\\\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:142px\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">吸水前质量</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">m</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">₁</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">/</span></span><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">g</span></span></span></span></span></p>\\n\\t\\t\\t</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td style=\\\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:142px\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td style=\\\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:142px\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td style=\\\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:142px\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">吸水现象</span></span></span></span></span></p>\\n\\t\\t\\t</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td style=\\\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:142px\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td style=\\\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:142px\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td style=\\\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:142px\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">吸水后质量</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">m</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">₂</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">/</span></span><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">g</span></span></span></span></span></p>\\n\\t\\t\\t</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td style=\\\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:142px\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t</td>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td style=\\\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:142px\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\">&nbsp;</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t</td>\\n\\t\\t</tr>\\n\\t\\t<tr>\\n\\t\\t\\t<td style=\\\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:142px\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p style=\\\"text-align:justify\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">吸水率</span></span></span><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5000pt\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\